{"tid":2396754,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句 地錯真係好麻麻","createTime":"2021-02-06T00:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T12:33:21.000Z","uid":254376,"like":10,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c18126a5a0c8f281e262c754b99ddff98d6be4","tid":2396754,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T00:50:04.000Z","msg":"對比起無職黎講根本差兩班，無論情感描寫好、人物性格好、打鬥畫面好，無職根本屌打。最重要既係，無職啲女正咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，地錯Hestia真係起唔到機，話就話大波蘿莉，但無職同樣蘿莉既Roxy見到就愛上左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n地錯我三季睇晒，無主線無焦點，好似見步行步咁，同當初講既目標偏離左。老實講睇晒成套嘢所謂既感動位真係谷唔到眼淚，熱血場面又令唔到我熱血，啲打鬥又係好普通，得最後牛兔打鬥先有啲睇頭，但又咁鬼姑寒打得果一陣，根本唔夠喉。整體黎講，呢套嘢唔係睇女既就無嘢好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\nBtw 套嘢係得劍姬同Freya真心覺得正，其他好似一樣樣咁，睇到好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf9271772db83d7c86412e29c945c1a9ecfd1f8","tid":2396754,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"利申：動畫黨，全部都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44888b31b0b2c99bca42141b015429078119e8cb","tid":2396754,"uid":254376,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"無職絕對屌打呢套地錯，淨係用左兩集就可以令觀眾流眼淚，節奏把握得好好，每件事都好有重點，目標都尚算明確。打鬥清晰流暢，魔法既動畫世一，震撼力強畫面好靚，水既動態好細緻。啲女都打爆地錯啲女，出Roxy一個都夠做。<br />\n<br />\n整體黎講，雖然暫時得4集，但足以勝過3季既地錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9ab361fa9251d7589ab98fa1b5d50fff808057","tid":2396754,"uid":18605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"制作組的錯<br />\n<br />\n動畫還原度來講無職高好多<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得兩者冇得咁拎來比較<br />\n<br />\n地錯係基於傳統rpg設定嘅王道類作品<br />\n無職就係一隻開放世界game<br />\n<br />\n龍與地下城同上古卷軸邊有得就咁拍埋來比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b910026d8460ef0e5acf75d87e12466c4c609c0b","tid":2396754,"uid":282446,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"地錯即係記錄地平線？"},{"pid":"a97c087ffd1766baa12961910d860c512576a49a","tid":2396754,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b910026d8460ef0e5acf75d87e12466c4c609c0b","tid":2396754,"uid":282446,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"地錯即係記錄地平線？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"在地下城尋找邂逅是否搞錯了什麼"},{"pid":"6f23be928421160882f7608f63aa20fc71f07a14","tid":2396754,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"得喇得喇 煩死人"},{"pid":"64554e65c805bd0a48aab4d5eb1ed35e68317d74","tid":2396754,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"無職出左4集d動畫黨以經周圍引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd76847472a875c72b5653f909190a95fa440d73","tid":2396754,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64554e65c805bd0a48aab4d5eb1ed35e68317d74","tid":2396754,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"無職出左4集d動畫黨以經周圍引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:57:35.000Z","msg":"唔明有乜好引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c334310bc8a576276665f8efe20e87d0175a07","tid":2396754,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f23be928421160882f7608f63aa20fc71f07a14","tid":2396754,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"得喇得喇 煩死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"ba5795624207b3a6aaf74c9bf12d926b2282e01a","tid":2396754,"uid":62950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd76847472a875c72b5653f909190a95fa440d73","tid":2396754,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64554e65c8